Global Network as a Service NaaS Market Insights
Network as a Service NaaS Market Market size was valued at USD 17.4 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 38.9 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.6% from 2024 to 2030.

Network as a Service (NaaS) Market Overview
The global Network as a Service (NaaS) market size was valued at USD 16.3 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 51.4 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 18.5% during the forecast period. The market is witnessing rapid growth due to the increasing demand for flexible, scalable, and cost-effective network infrastructure solutions. NaaS offers businesses a pay-per-use model, enhancing operational efficiency and reducing capital expenditure. This transformation is driven by the proliferation of cloud-based solutions, growing adoption of IoT, and the shift toward digital transformation in enterprises worldwide.

